      • findByMissionCodeAndProductTypeAndSensingStartTimeLessAndSensingStopTimeGreater

        @Query("select p from Product p where p.productClass.mission.code = ?1 and p.productClass.productType = ?2 and p.sensingStartTime <= ?3 and p.sensingStopTime >= ?4")
